{"tid":1623252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］十月五，全新行動方案","createTime":"2019-10-04T19:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T20:52:15.000Z","uid":24648,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a53f3c4ac6ecc21fed87d977a4d5ac96865a1b3","tid":1623252,"uid":24648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:17:12.000Z","msg":"就係全民留家訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先聽聽我講，原因有二<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因一</span></span></strong>基本上地鐵全封，各大商場關門，已經達到死城效果，宵禁咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />何不輕輕一推比文宣同新聞做一下緊急法後帶來嘅香港死城景象。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">而原因二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>本人嘅推測係，由於地鐵全封，如果10.5都十八區開花有行動嘅話由於冇交通，好大機會手足會係自己區開，咁樣會有利於popo知道各區手足比例同行動，同時<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">容易target手足</span></span>身處係邊一區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />何不休息返一日，睇外界回應嘅同時留返日補補mp魔法呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對抗極權要長期抗爭，急不在一時<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，反抗！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e98ece20612045d13643d782f7dba2713a0e1087","tid":1623252,"uid":24648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:19:56.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"7f14eb27be31a8354deb20f387254f734225782e","tid":1623252,"uid":24648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:20:08.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547c8d9de42916ef411444e31c8fe12579bfd776","tid":1623252,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:20:22.000Z","msg":"唔急，等明年十一再上街啦。"},{"pid":"8c6499b9dce0d14e2ebec21d891c4